\"\\\"Whatever you are facing right now-it's not the end of your story.\", \"from\": 620, \"to\": 686, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"God is with you and always will be.\", \"from\": 687, \"to\": 722, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Thank you to everyone who believes that the Kenyan sprint story will never be the same again,\\\" wrote Omanyala on his Instagram.\", \"from\": 724, \"to\": 852, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 842, \"end\": 851, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 0.9999999999697593, \"rank\": 3.0222219300533465e-11, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kenya has for a long time been a powerhouse in long-distance races but Omanyala tore the script and placed the country on the global map in the 100m dash.\", \"from\": 854, \"to\": 1008, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 854, \"end\": 859, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"score\": 0.9999999999686224, \"rank\": 3.092801256919432e-11, \"text\": \"Kenya\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His followers congratulated him for carrying Kenya's flag high despite, urging him to keep his chin up.\", \"from\": 1010, \"to\": 1113, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1055, \"end\": 1060, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"score\": 0.9999999999686224, \"rank\": 3.092801256919432e-11, \"text\": \"Kenya\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Azziad:You are a champ.\", \"from\": 1115, \"to\": 1138, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ekodydda:9.79, remember that is your time.\", \"from\": 1140, \"to\": 1182, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not forget that  Tracy Waithera:You are amazing